Uses of Package
CommonLib.common

  • Packages that use CommonLib.common 
    Package Description
    CommonLib.common
    'common' package contains interfaces and classes that do not stand alone and can be used in any project.
    ServerSide.db
    'db' package contains the classes that responsible on the communication with the database.
    ServerSide.server
    'server' package contains the application entry point, and some functionalities like configuration and connectivity.
